      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.lX8x7huS9M0gGIcr]{Kalistocrat}</p>\n<p>Your daily meditation keeps your body and mind in sync, but certain devotions allow you to focus on different areas of your body. Each day, choose one of the following feats for which you meet the prerequisites as a bonus feat: @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.UwmeR3lCfm936vxe]{Great Fortitude}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.d7o4eg6e0xgstNfQ]{Iron Will}, or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.bTzOH89OmNana18M]{Lightning Reflexes}. This choice is made after a 10-minute meditation following an 8-hour rest and can only be changed once every 24 hours.</p>"
